{"tid":2094183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「加拿大暫停加港引渡協議」是向香港發出法治死亡證","createTime":"2020-07-04T11:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:00:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5910c40c6d17630f48e72031920beaf27fd54d00","tid":2094183,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"一個司法管轄區與另一司法管轄區簽訂引渡協議, <br />\n意即係認同對方同本國有相同程度既法治, 係有公平審訊<br />\n如果認為對方係無法治, 有如北韓赤柬之類, 係唔會為對方係自己境內拘捕及移交至海外的<br />\n係唔會簽訂引渡協議<br />\n<br />\n所以, 「加拿大暫停加港引渡協議」是向香港發出法治死亡證<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200703/s00001/1593789923142/港區國安法-加拿大暫停加港引渡協議-禁出口敏感軍用品到香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200703%2Fs00001%2F1593789923142%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwms%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=f7c1b45a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200703%2Fs00001%2F1593789923142%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%BB%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&h=4b7cba4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200703/s00001/1593789923142/港區國安法-加拿大暫停加港引渡協議-禁出口敏感軍用品到香港</a><br />\n<br />\n《港區國安法》生效，加拿大周五（3日）宣布，會暫停與香港之間的引渡協議。加拿大外長商鵬飛（Fran&ccedil;ois-Philippe Champagne）發表聲明表示，禁止出口敏感軍用品到香港。<br />\n<br />\n商鵬飛譴責《港區國安法》以「遮遮掩掩的」（secretive）方式實施，稱加拿大是被迫重新評估現有對港安排。他又說，加國會視出口到香港的敏感物品，如同出口到中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n加國總理杜魯多表示，正考慮就香港推出包括移民在內的更多措施，但未有透露詳情。"},{"pid":"3ff08bc685f5879f6a078dd15290be747311050b","tid":2094183,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Everything is stacking up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff2d12492e6f046cb0c87a9d926d5bbc94a5919","tid":2094183,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"OMDB講兩句?"}]}